Package: datomanager
Title: Governance and Access Management for datom Data Repositories
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Afshin", "Mashadi-Hossein", , "amashadihossein@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Companion governance package for datom. Owns the governed
    lifecycle of datom data repositories -- governance repo bootstrap,
    project registration, dispatch routing, managed data migration, and
    decommissioning -- plus reader-facing access enforcement (roles,
    grants, and IAM-backed storage access points). datomanager depends on
    datom and orchestrates datom's exported platform helpers; datom never
    depends on datomanager and remains fully functional without it.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/amashadihossein/datomanager
BugReports: https://github.com/amashadihossein/datomanager/issues
